\[\bm{a}-\bm{x}_{0}=\frac{1}{1-t}(a-\bm{x}_{t}).\]

_Therefore, \(\bm{a}-\bm{x}_{0}\) is deterministically decided by \(\bm{x}_{t}\) and \(s\). This yields_

